correspondent, Margaret
Warner, begins our coverage.

01:32.725 --> 01:38.798 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: The warnings
started at the
demilitarized zone dividing the
Koreas, where

01:38.832 --> 01:43.136 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
