shrink from
military action.

01:54.247 --> 01:57.083 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE PENCE, Vice President of
the United States:
The world witnessed the strength
and resolve

01:57.117 --> 02:02.956 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of our new president in actions
taken in Syria
and Afghanistan.

02:02.989 --> 02:08.728 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
North Korea would do well not to
test his
resolve or the strength of the
armed forces

02:08.761 --> 02:10.663 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
