region.

02:10.697 --> 02:16.402 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: Mr. Pence also
declared again
that the U.S. and its allies
will act, unless

02:16.436 --> 02:20.373 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
