took a moment
out from the White House Easter
egg roll to

02:24.777 --> 02:26.880 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
send his own briefing warning.

02:26.913 --> 02:28.548 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
QUESTION: Any message for North
Korea?

02:28.581 --> 02:31.284 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States:
Got to behave.

02:31.317 --> 02:36.256 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: But at the
United Nations,
the deputy ambassador from North
Korea, officially

02:36.289 --> 02:39.759 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the Democratic People's Republic
of Korea,
or DPRK, was defiant.

02:39.792 --> 02:42.729 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
®MD-BO /KIM IN RYONG, Deputy
North Korean
Ambassador to the United
Nations: The DPRK

02:42.762 --> 02:49.202 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
