war desired
by the Americans.

02:49.235 --> 02:53.606 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: The dueling
rhetoric came
after North Korea's ballistic
missile launch

02:53.640 --> 02:59.512 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
