minister told
the BBC that his government will
be testing

03:20.333 --> 03:26.573 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
missiles weekly, and he warned
of a preemptive
nuclear strike by the North if
the U.S. takes

03:26.606 --> 03:28.575 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
military action.

03:28.608 --> 03:32.111 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Opinions among South Koreans
seem sharply
divided.

03:32.145 --> 03:36.983 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): As
Trump became
president, the policies seem
likely to become

03:37.016 --> 03:40.653 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
more oppressive, and it worries
me that war
might actually break out.

03:40.687 --> 03:45.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): In
fact, I believe
we have to strongly respond to
North Korea's

03:45.592 --> 03:47.360 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
provocation.

03:47.393 --> 03:51.464 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: Mr. Pence today
echoed other
top officials in saying the
Obama era policy

03:51.497 --> 03:54.634 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of strategic patience with the
North is over.

03:54.667 --> 04:00.707 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
