Margaret Warner.

04:03.876 --> 04:08.948 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In the day's
other news: Wall
Street rallied broadly after the
weekend passed

04:08.982 --> 04:11.517 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
