how seriously

11:03.329 --> 11:05.064 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
they will negotiate.

11:05.097 --> 11:09.669 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I'm not recommending military
action, but
I think that the threat of
military action

11:09.702 --> 11:11.971 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
has become credible to North
Korea now.

11:12.004 --> 11:15.307 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
