11:15.341 --> 11:21.747 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And you see the
leadership
in the North, Kim Jong-un, the
people around

11:21.781 --> 11:26.218 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
