rationally
about this?

11:26.252 --> 11:32.658 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM PERRY: I think that the
regime in
North Korea today is not crazy.

11:32.692 --> 11:35.895 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
