assuredly has been
effective for many decades now,
is to preserve

11:41.000 --> 11:42.835 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
their regime and power.

11:42.868 --> 11:48.741 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's what they're trying to
do, and that's
their calculus and it's a
rational calculus.

11:48.774 --> 11:50.576 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We need to respond to that.

11:50.609 --> 11:54.513 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we do not -- if we think
they're crazy,
