to military
action, a misinterpretation?

12:16.135 --> 12:23.342 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM PERRY: The reason I do
not favor military
action now is because, once a
military action

12:23.375 --> 12:27.213 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
starts, it will get out -- it
will escalate,
and is all too easy to get out
of control.

12:27.246 --> 12:30.916 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It could escalate on to a total
general war.

12:30.950 --> 12:36.122 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's a war which North Korea
would, in fact,
lose, but as they were losing
it, and as they

12:36.155 --> 12:39.825 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
saw their regime being swept
away and their
country being devastated, they
might then

12:39.859 --> 12:46.332 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
use nuclear weapons, one last
dangerous, but
one last sort of an Armageddon,
before they

12:46.365 --> 12:48.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
were swept out of power.

12:48.134 --> 12:51.637 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, the danger of nuclear war
here is not
that North Korea would
deliberately start

12:51.670 --> 12:55.841 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
one and provoke like a surprise
attack on
South Korea.

12:55.875 --> 13:01.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The danger is that we would
blunder in a nuclear
war by a military conflict, a
conventional

13:01.447 --> 13:04.784 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
military conflict and a
conventional war escalating
into that.

13:04.817 --> 13:08.154 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Finally, how
worried should
the American people be about
this?

13:08.187 --> 13:12.091 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM PERRY: I am very
alarmed.

13:12.124 --> 13:18.030 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I'm alarmed because, if we move
into a military
action, even a minor military
action, the

13:18.063 --> 13:19.765 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
danger of escalation, I think,
is very great.

13:19.799 --> 13:21.901 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
