well escalate into a general war
and even

13:33.045 --> 13:34.013 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
a nuclear war.

13:34.046 --> 13:36.615 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I'm concerned for that
reason.

13:36.649 --> 13:38.450 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
