politics since the founding of
the modern

14:12.251 --> 14:14.186 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
republic.

14:14.220 --> 14:18.457 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Among the most significant
changes, a transition
from a parliamentary to a
presidential system

14:18.490 --> 14:23.028 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that could lead to a major
consolidation of
power by the nation's leader.

14:23.062 --> 14:25.431 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
