14:25.464 --> 14:32.504 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Flag-waving
supporters greeted
Turkish President Recep Tayyip
Erdogan in

14:32.538 --> 14:36.542 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
