14:36.575 --> 14:39.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RECEP TAYYIP ERDOGAN, Turkish
President (through
translator): We have put up a
fight against

14:39.912 --> 14:41.947 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
