us.

14:47.286 --> 14:48.254 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We didn't succumb.

14:48.287 --> 14:50.256 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
As a nation, we stood strong.

14:50.289 --> 14:54.760 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But amid the
celebration, questions
about the vote's validity.

14:54.793 --> 14:59.932 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Turkey's main opposition party
