15:31.163 --> 15:36.402 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It authorizes constitutional
changes allowing
the president to directly name
government

15:36.435 --> 15:41.173 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ministers and other senior
officials, appoint
half the members of the
country's highest

15:41.206 --> 15:46.478 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
