executive president.

16:08.133 --> 16:12.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Erdogan says the
changes will
bring stability, in a country
battling the

16:12.504 --> 16:16.275 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
