16:38.564 --> 16:41.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SIGMAR GABRIEL, German Foreign
Minister (through
translator): We will only be
able to help

16:41.333 --> 16:44.169 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Turkey if the country stays on a
