18:11.957 --> 18:13.058 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
KADIR USTUN: Sure, yes.

18:13.092 --> 18:14.893 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Because this was
