new constitution.

18:46.391 --> 18:48.660 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Turkish prime minister had
been the head
of the government.

18:48.694 --> 18:51.964 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The locus of power had been with
the prime
minister.

18:51.997 --> 18:57.069 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The president had a number of
important powers,
