19:21.727 --> 19:23.896 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So it's in that range.

19:23.929 --> 19:25.531 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But this was about the
referendum.

19:25.564 --> 19:27.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This was about the system
change.

19:27.566 --> 19:34.873 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
