we should
go to a presidential system and
whether what

19:47.286 --> 19:51.323 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Erdogan is proposing is the way
to go.

19:51.356 --> 19:52.691 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And they voted yes.

19:52.724 --> 19:57.362 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: What do you see
in the lower
vote than expected?

19:57.396 --> 20:02.301 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVEN COOK: Well, it was an
extraordinarily
controversial move to
fundamentally alter

20:02.334 --> 20:04.336 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Turkey's political system.

20:04.369 --> 20:07.606 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And there is about half the
