horrific
homicide.

36:35.393 --> 36:41.699 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, Facebook has an incentive to
not make
us not want to upload things,
which they may

36:41.732 --> 36:43.634 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
