36:43.668 --> 36:48.239 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You can imagine the outcry of
people on Facebook
if you went to upload a video,
and it didn't

36:48.272 --> 36:52.310 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
