Facebook was waiting
to approve it.

36:52.343 --> 36:57.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
People wouldn't like that
either, but nor
do we like having videos like
this in our

36:57.215 --> 36:58.482 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
timeline.

36:58.516 --> 37:00.418 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, it's a really tough
challenge for them
to walk that line.

37:00.451 --> 37:02.186 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And also -- we have
about a minute
