their Facebook
Live feature.

37:04.522 --> 37:06.190 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
EMILY DREYFUSS: Yes.

37:06.224 --> 37:09.694 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Now, this was a video
