37:11.629 --> 37:15.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What's this going to do to their
efforts to
boost Facebook Live?

37:15.566 --> 37:17.501 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
EMILY DREYFUSS: Yes.

37:17.535 --> 37:22.406 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With Facebook Live, what was, as
