37:24.208 --> 37:29.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Unless they were to put Facebook
Live on a
delay, and it would cease to be
live, there

37:29.180 --> 37:32.483 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
is no way that they can avoid
things like
this from hitting the site.

37:32.516 --> 37:36.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's honestly a miracle that
homicides
and horrible, gruesome violence
have not been

37:37.021 --> 37:38.823 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
