37:38.856 --> 37:44.128 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's something that Facebook
has to know,
and it's deciding that it can
depend on its

37:44.161 --> 37:47.531 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
users to flag content soon
enough to take
it down.

37:47.565 --> 37:51.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But it is definitely taking that
risk in order
to push this product that is
live.

37:51.936 --> 37:55.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Emily Dreyfuss on the
