He's raised a ton of money, and
enthusiasm
among the Democratic base, while
the Republican

39:41.879 --> 39:43.247 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
base not quite as enthusiastic.

39:43.280 --> 39:45.583 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, these are the
factors at
play here.

39:45.616 --> 39:48.986 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, this is different from the
Kansas race
that we watched last week.

39:49.019 --> 39:51.989 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: This
is, because it's closer.

39:52.022 --> 39:52.990 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
