been able
to sort of consolidate
Democratic support.

40:00.765 --> 40:05.970 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the Republicans are sort of
fighting each
other as much as they're
fighting him.

40:06.003 --> 40:09.907 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He -- this Democrat, Jon Ossoff,
is an interesting
candidate.

40:09.940 --> 40:14.545 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's a young person, not really
any political
experience.

40:14.578 --> 40:17.081 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's running for Congress for
the first time.

40:17.114 --> 40:22.887 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
